## Bench Constraints (apply everywhere)

- **Never edit** `apps/{frappe,erpnext,crm,hrms,lending,lms,education,helpdesk,gameplan,drive,press}/` — upstream, read-only.
- Custom work lives in `apps/{novizna_crm,novizna_core,novizna_pos,invoice_ninja_integration,noviznaerp_payroll,cargo_management,changemakers,erpnext_location}/`.
- Never read `sites/<site>/site_config.json` or `.env` **values** into context. Key names only.
- Never push to a git remote without typed confirmation of the host.
- `bench restart` requires typing the **site name** (`{{ bench.primary_site }}`), not "yes".
- Type annotations + PEP 257 docstrings on every Python function.
- No `frappe.db.commit()` inside `doc_events`. No f-string interpolation in `frappe.db.sql` — use `values=`.

